Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.52,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[ Applause ]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.11,0:00:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello everybody, thank you for
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.61,0:00:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,coming this evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.12,0:00:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Last session of the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.16,0:00:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here to talk about what's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.52,0:00:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,new in Wallet and Apple Pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.80,0:00:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And there are three things that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.31,0:00:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to talk about.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.21,0:00:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to break today's
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,session down to three sections.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.04,0:00:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The first one is going to be a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.92,0:00:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,little bit about the Apply Pay
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.12,0:00:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.34,0:00:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Some of you might be familiar
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.70,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with Apple Pay, but we've also
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.22,0:00:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,been quite busy this past year,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so we're going to run through
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,some of the new things we've
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,been doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.23,0:00:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we're going to look at iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.53,0:00:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,11 and macOS High Sierra and
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.75,0:01:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to talk about what's
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.90,0:01:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,new with Apple Pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.40,0:01:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, finally, we're going
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,to look at some of the new API
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.76,0:01:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,inside of Wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.22,0:01:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, there are a few things
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we're not going to cover in this
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.83,0:01:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,session.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not going to cover getting
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.38,0:01:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,started with the Apply Pay API
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.42,0:01:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,and how you integrate Apple Pay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with your payment processor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.79,0:01:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We have a lot of great resources
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.38,0:01:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,for that, you can check out last
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.02,0:01:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,year's WWDC sessions, "Apply Pay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.03,0:01:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on the Web," and "What's New
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.61,0:01:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With Wallet and Apple Pay" 2016
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.79,0:01:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,for more information.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's dive right in and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,let's talk about the Apply Pay
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.66,0:01:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, hopefully many of you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.82,0:01:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,who've used Apple Pay either in
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,a store, or in an app, or on the
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.12,0:01:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,web, and if you have, you'll
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.30,0:01:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,know that Apple Pay is easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.62,0:01:51.61,Default,,0,0,0,,secure, and private way to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.17,0:01:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And when we first launched Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.52,0:01:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay in iOS 8, we supported
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.57,0:02:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,payments within applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's a good example.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But, since then we've expanded
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.93,0:02:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pay to far more places.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We've expanded it to Safari.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.80,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You can now make payments from
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.03,0:02:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Safari on mac and on iOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.48,0:02:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,We've also expanded it to Siri.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.89,0:02:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make payments now from
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.73,0:02:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,within SiriKit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Another great extension point
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.44,0:02:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,we've added Apple Pay to is
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,messages, you can write messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,apps that can take advantage of
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.27,0:02:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pay directly from within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.74,0:02:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the message's application.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.98,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy a movie ticket and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,send it to a friend without ever
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,having to leave the messages
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.85,0:02:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,app.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And finally, we've added support
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.94,0:02:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,for watchOS.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make payments within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.38,0:02:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,watchOS on WatchKit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Last year, we also added
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.82,0:02:52.18,Default,,0,0,0,,support, natively on the new Mac
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Book Pro with Touch Bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now you can make payments
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,directly on your Mac without
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.38,0:02:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,handing them off to an iOS
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.69,0:02:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,device.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:03:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And hopefully you've also had a
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.90,0:03:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,chance to see some of the apps
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.18,0:03:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that have been built on top of
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,WatchKit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The Apple Store is a great
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,example.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.39,0:03:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You can buy accessories directly
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,from your wrist.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.56,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You just pick an accessory, pick
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,a card, and you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, when we first launched
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.23,0:03:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pay it was only available
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.55,0:03:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,in the United States, but since
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.82,0:03:20.31,Default,,0,0,0,,then we've been extremely busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In the past year alone, we've
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.32,0:03:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,launched in over a dozen new
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.77,0:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Here are all the countries that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.11,0:03:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,we're currently supported in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.75,0:03:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,One country that I'm
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,particularly excited about is
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.89,0:03:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In Japan, you can actually use
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.17,0:03:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pay directly on the Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.15,0:03:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Transit System with your Suica
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.73,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Card.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.04,0:03:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It works really, really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing we launched last
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.38,0:03:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,year after WWDC was Apple Pay
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.40,0:03:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,for nonprofits.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really interesting if
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you're a nonprofit and you want
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to take Apple Pay either within
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,your application, or perhaps on
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,your website.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.59,0:03:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's an example from OXFAM in
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,the United Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're one of the largest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.44,0:04:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,nonprofits in the UK and they
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,actually found that using Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay reduced the time that it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.80,0:04:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,took to get a donation from 2
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,minutes to 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.85,0:04:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a huge decrease.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And as a result, they're seeing
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,much better user experience and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you're interested in
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.42,0:04:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,accepting Apple Pay as a
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.15,0:04:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,nonprofit, it's really easy to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use it inside of your
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,apps and on the web.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.73,0:04:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And to help support you, we've
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,added a new donate with Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay button style.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.31,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a very simple signup
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.70,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,process.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.69,0:04:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find out more about
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where this is supported and how
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.34,0:04:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,to get started at the developer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,site.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.03,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, if you're not using Apple
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.07,0:04:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay, you might be wondering why
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,should I adapt it in my app or
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,on the web.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Apple Pay is one of the best
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.70,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,ways for users to pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It has one of the highest
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,customer satisfaction ratings of
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.34,0:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,any wallet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.95,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's also the best way for
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:04:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,merchants to be paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.33,0:05:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to illustrate that with a
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,little example of a typical
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,product flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,So, normally in the checkout
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,process, we buy a product.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.93,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We go to a website, we got to an
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.70,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,app, we see the product and we
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,add it to our cart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we go to checkout.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.35,0:05:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And the first thing we normally
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,have to do is we have to create
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.44,0:05:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,an account, or sight in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I don't have an account,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I've got to like create
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.26,0:05:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,one and then go to my email to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.61,0:05:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,verify it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.91,0:05:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, I've left the site already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I come back and I've
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.11,0:05:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,got to add my shipping address.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And then once I add my shipping
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.81,0:05:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,address, well I shipped it to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.35,0:05:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,work, and my credit card uses my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.07,0:05:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,home address as my billing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.24,0:05:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, now I've got to add my
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,billing address.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,And I've got to type in my card
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.47,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Except, I left my credit card on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.06,0:05:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,the other side of the stage, so
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,now I've got to go over there to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.99,0:05:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,get the CVV number on the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,And then I've got to review the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And then finally I can confirm
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.27,0:05:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's not really surprising
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.68,0:06:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that if you've done any
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.51,0:06:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ecommerce work, conversion rates
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.98,0:06:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of the biggest things you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,encounter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.02,0:06:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Users drop off all the time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.83,0:06:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,during purchase.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But, with Apple Pay, it's so
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.49,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,much simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.64,0:06:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You just tap or click the buy
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,with Apple Pay button, and
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.79,0:06:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these steps are coalesced
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.23,0:06:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,into a single user experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.02,0:06:24.31,Default,,0,0,0,,And this has some really
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.31,0:06:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,dramatic results for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.64,0:06:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.09,0:06:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Over the past three years, we've
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,been asking merchants what they
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.27,0:06:33.28,Default,,0,0,0,,found with Apple Pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,And they've told us that they've
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.01,0:06:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,seen between 2 and 5 times
